{{Chalukyas|Vengi}}
'''Indra Bhattaraka''' (673 CE) succeeded his brother [[Jayasimha I (Eastern Chalukya dynasty)|Jayasimha I]] as the king of Eastern Chalukyas. He had a very short reign of a week.

His son [[Vishnuvardhana II]] succeeded him.

